{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/memasang-openjdk-11-ubuntu/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Openjdk merupakan set tools dasar untuk pengembangan aplikasi berbasis java. Untuk memasangnya di OS Ubuntu caranya sangat mudah karena Openjdk 11 sudah tersedia di repository utama Ubuntu 18.04.</p>\n<p>Pertama lakukan <code class=\"language-text\">apt update</code> untuk memastikan Ubuntu telah memiliki daftar paket terbaru dari repository</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> update</code></pre></div>\n<p>Gunakan perintah berikut untuk mengetahui openjdk versi berapa saja yang tersedia di repository Ubuntu Bionic</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">apt-cache</span> search openjdk</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a1e931eb7fb562cc16fcc4abfafa36fc/ad00e/openjdk-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"SS Openjdk 1\"\n        title=\"SS Openjdk 1\"\n        src=\"/static/a1e931eb7fb562cc16fcc4abfafa36fc/5a190/openjdk-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a1e931eb7fb562cc16fcc4abfafa36fc/772e8/openjdk-1.png 200w,\n/static/a1e931eb7fb562cc16fcc4abfafa36fc/e17e5/openjdk-1.png 400w,\n/static/a1e931eb7fb562cc16fcc4abfafa36fc/5a190/openjdk-1.png 800w,\n/static/a1e931eb7fb562cc16fcc4abfafa36fc/c1b63/openjdk-1.png 1200w,\n/static/a1e931eb7fb562cc16fcc4abfafa36fc/ad00e/openjdk-1.png 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Untuk memasang Openjdk versi 11 gunakan perintah</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> openjdk-11-jdk</code></pre></div>\n<p>Terakhir pastikan <code class=\"language-text\">java</code> dan <code class=\"language-text\">javac</code> memiliki angka versi yang sama</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">javac --version\njava --version</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2559ec49d24cbceef31532a1bff54e98/ad00e/openjdk-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"SS Openjdk 2\"\n        title=\"SS Openjdk 2\"\n        src=\"/static/2559ec49d24cbceef31532a1bff54e98/5a190/openjdk-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2559ec49d24cbceef31532a1bff54e98/772e8/openjdk-2.png 200w,\n/static/2559ec49d24cbceef31532a1bff54e98/e17e5/openjdk-2.png 400w,\n/static/2559ec49d24cbceef31532a1bff54e98/5a190/openjdk-2.png 800w,\n/static/2559ec49d24cbceef31532a1bff54e98/c1b63/openjdk-2.png 1200w,\n/static/2559ec49d24cbceef31532a1bff54e98/ad00e/openjdk-2.png 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Selesai.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Memasang Openjdk 11 di Ubuntu 18.04"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/memasang-openjdk-11-ubuntu/"}}}